&lt;li&gt;Support Content Manager in the planning, scheduling, and publishing of content across social media platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist the Content Manager in maintaining social content calendars, ensuring alignment with brand priorities&lt;/li&gt;
